ZH: 我的故乡是一个美丽的小村庄。
EN: My hometown is a beautiful small village.

ZH: 我们每年回故乡过春节。
EN: We go back to our hometown for Chinese New Year every year.

ZH: 我的故乡有着丰富的文化遗产。
EN: My hometown has rich cultural heritage.

ZH: 故乡的风景让人心旷神怡。
EN: The scenery of my hometown is refreshing.

ZH: 我想念故乡的家乡味。
EN: I miss the hometown flavors.

ZH: 故乡的人们都十分友好。
EN: The people in my hometown are very friendly.

ZH: 故乡的农民正在收割庄稼。
EN: The farmers in my hometown are harvesting crops.

ZH: 在故乡长大对我来说是一种幸运。
EN: Growing up in my hometown is a blessing for me.

ZH: 故乡的地势比较平坦。
EN: The terrain in my hometown is relatively flat.

ZH: 我的家人都住在故乡。
EN: My family all live in the hometown.

ZH: 故乡的雨水很充沛。
EN: The rainfall in my hometown is abundant.

ZH: 我们在故乡度过了一个愉快的暑假。
EN: We spent a pleasant summer vacation in our hometown.

ZH: 故乡的夜晚非常安静。
EN: The nights in my hometown are very quiet.

ZH: 故乡的建筑风格很有特色。
EN: The architectural style of my hometown is very distinctive.

ZH: 我的故乡是一个海滨城市。
EN: My hometown is a coastal city.

ZH: 故乡的风俗习惯很有趣。
EN: The customs and traditions of my hometown are very interesting.

ZH: 我的父母住在故乡的老房子里。
EN: My parents live in an old house in the hometown.

ZH: 故乡的人们热情好客。
EN: The people in my hometown are hospitable.

ZH: 我在故乡的小学上学过。
EN: I went to primary school in my hometown.

ZH: 故乡的美食让人垂涎欲滴。
EN: The delicious food in my hometown makes people drool.
